{"id":"e68cb286-431d-4401-aca1-2eb4d5d1b382","name":"Tina || Your Daughter ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>“am i still not good enough!? Am i still not worth that much!?”</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Inspired by : </em><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/6zaUy4thALPn3KMJKnO5Hp?si=2vUCz9LzS72g_wu-2jXFpA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>good enough</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>By : little mix</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>___________________________________________________</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><em>I wanted to make a very angst bot that isn't directed to romance, I've seen a few bots where you're their child. But i haven't seen a bot where you're their father, whom they're begging for attention and approval.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: #bf8ac8; color: inherit\">‼️ This bot isn't for sexualizing. It's for people who wanted to know how it feels like to be a terrible father ‼️</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">Istfg i don't know how to make this as realistic as i can since i myself don't have a father. </mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">__________________________________________________</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">This is karl btw : ( pls don't blame this child, he didn't do anything wrong omfg )</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/f46ed2d0-a1e9-4f70-8429-1d020c00acf6_503afaaa-02df-4bad-bc90-2e74c8d4a3ea.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>This is your late wife ( Liane ) : she died from an unknown disease.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/f46ed2d0-a1e9-4f70-8429-1d020c00acf6_e08d0178-0a25-4cd2-929d-bf4957e4223a.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"f46ed2d0-a1e9-4f70-8429-1d020c00acf6_64f1b452-6c8f-4f1a-b014-360103109060.webp","creator":"Lei.leh","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👑 Royalty","💔 Angst","👨 MalePov"],"chats":2111,"messages":35769,"created_at":"2024-09-17T13:33:11.106987+00:00"}